name: Frederica Baumann
description:
Would appreciate images, feeedback, requests, reviews, and of course comments in the comments. Please check out my other models if you like this one.

personal prefernce for model version, V3 is not objectively better, make sure to pick which one you think looks best

Frederica Baumann from Re:zero. trained on abyssorangemix2

recommended weights 0.6 - 1.0

Recommended tags: frederica_baumann, green_eyes, long_hair, roswaal mansion_maid_uniform, large_breasts,

optional: sharp_teeth (usually doesn't look well without editing photo), animal ears,tail, Tiger transformation (not the full thing, but adds a tail and ears)

had to go through a few hours of failures and studying Lora guides and such to get this looking decent, so hope you all enjoy, and hopefully i can make better Loras and upgrade previous ones.

the towel image was made with this prompt;

positive: best quality, highres,ultra-detailed, 1girl, solo_focus, <lora:FredericaV4:1.0>, Frederica, frederica_baumann, blonde hair, green eyes, long_hair, towel, wet_hair, after shower, large_breasts.

negative: (painting by bad-artist:0.8), (painting by bad-artist-anime:0.8), bad-image-9600, Unspeakable-Horrors-Composition-4v, NG_DeepNegative_V1_2T, (easynegative:1.2), lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry, artist name, lower_teeth

then sent to img2img and using the same prompt i changed samplers and multiplied the original width and height by 1.5.
